name: Denti-Cal
description: Denti-Cal is California's Medicaid dental program, providing comprehensive dental care to Medi-Cal beneficiaries at no cost, helping ensure oral health for low-income individuals and families.
fullDescription: Denti-Cal is California's Medicaid dental program, providing comprehensive dental care to Medi-Cal beneficiaries at no cost, helping ensure oral health for low-income individuals and families.
whatTheyOffer:
- Preventive care (cleanings, exams, x-rays)
- Restorative services (fillings, crowns)
- Extractions and oral surgery
- Dentures and partials
- Emergency dental services
- Orthodontics for children under 21 (when medically necessary)
howToGetIt: If you have Medi-Cal, you automatically have Denti-Cal. Find a Denti-Cal provider using the online provider search or call the Denti-Cal hotline at 1-800-322-6384.
